---
const title = "Studio Batterie 🥁";
---

<html lang="fr">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<title>{title}</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<a href="/methode-musique/" class="back-link">← Retour aux instruments</a>

		<main class="welcome-container">
			<header class="hero">
				<span class="emoji">🥁</span>
				<h1>{title}</h1>
				<p class="subtitle">Prêt à faire trembler les murs ? Choisis ton parcours !</p>
			</header>

			<div class="choices-grid">
				<!-- Option Enfants -->
				<a href="/methode-musique/batterie/enfant" class="card card-enfant">
					<div class="card-content">
						<span class="card-emoji">🦊</span>
						<h2>Parcours Enfants</h2>
						<p>Des rythmes amusants, des jeux d'animaux et de la coordination ludique !</p>
						<span class="btn">C'est parti !</span>
					</div>
				</a>

				<!-- Option Adultes -->
				<a href="/methode-musique/batterie/adulte" class="card card-adulte">
					<div class="card-content">
						<span class="card-emoji">⚡</span>
						<h2>Parcours Adultes</h2>
						<p>Une méthode de groove directe, de l'indépendance physique et des playbacks.</p>
						<span class="btn">Découvrir le programme</span>
					</div>
				</a>
			</div>
		</main>
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	:root {
		--bg-dark: #0b0f19;
		--card-bg: #111827;
		--accent-enfant: #10b981; /* Vert dynamique */
		--accent-adulte: #f59e0b; /* Orange batterie */
		--text-light: #ffffff;
		--text-muted: #9ca3af;
	}

	* { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

	body {
		background-color: var(--bg-dark);
		color: var(--text-light);
		font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
		min-height: 100vh;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		padding: 20px;
	}

	.back-link {
		align-self: flex-start;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		text-decoration: none;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		margin-bottom: 20px;
		transition: color 0.2s;
	}
	.back-link:hover { color: var(--accent-adulte); }

	.welcome-container { max-width: 900px; width: 100%; text-align: center; }
	.hero { margin-bottom: 40px; }
	.emoji { font-size: 4rem; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 10px; }
	
	h1 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		margin-bottom: 15px;
		background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--accent-adulte), #f43f5e);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
	}

	.subtitle { font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--text-muted); }
	.choices-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 30px; margin-top: 20px; }

	.card {
		background-color: var(--card-bg);
		border-radius: 20px;
		text-decoration: none;
		color: inherit;
		overflow: hidden;
		transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
		border: 1px solid #1f2937;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		height: 100%;
	}
	.card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); }
	.card-enfant:hover { box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.15); border-color: var(--accent-enfant); }
	.card-adulte:hover { box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.15); border-color: var(--accent-adulte); }

	.card-content { padding: 40px 30px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; height: 100%; gap: 15px; }
	.card-emoji { font-size: 3rem; }
	h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; }
	p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 15px; }
	
	.btn { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 25px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.95rem; width: 100%; text-align: center; }
	.card-enfant .btn { background-color: var(--accent-enfant); color: #0b0f19; }
	.card-adulte .btn { background-color: var(--accent-adulte); color: #0b0f19; }
</style>